WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.318
The bedrock of all effective leadership is self-awareness. Before leading

00:00:04.318 --> 00:00:08.636
a global matrix organization, it is necessary to be intimately

00:00:08.636 --> 00:00:12.955
aware of internal cognitive and emotional architecture. Consciousness of self

00:00:12.955 --> 00:00:17.273
is the ability to acknowledge internal thoughts, feelings, and reactions,

00:00:17.273 --> 00:00:21.591
as well as external behaviors.
